*User Story*

As the engineering team, we want to build a monitoring dashboard in HC so that we can actively track the performance, success rate, and failure rate of the new user segmentation and redirection logic implemented on the Legacy Factorform website ({{factor75.com/factorform}}) immediately after launch.
{panel}

{panel:bgColor=#e3fcef}
*Acceptance Criteria*

# *Total Checks:* The dashboard must display a metric tracking the Total redirect checks triggered
# *Successful Redirects :* The dashboard must display the Percentage of successful redirects (i.e., the percentage of unregistered users on legacy FactorForm correctly sent to Shopify FactorForm)
# *Successful No-Redirects:* The dashboard must display the Successful no-redirects metric (i.e., the percentage of registered users on legacy FactorForm correctly *not* directed to Shopify FactorForm)
# *API Failures:* The dashboard must display a metric tracking API failures (where the email validation endpoint fails to return either registered or unregistered status)
# *Dashboard Creation:* A new board must be created in Honeycomb specifically for monitoring the Legacy website redirection metrics mentioned above.
{panel}

