*Description*

Create an OTP checkout specific hook {{useCreateOTPCartForCheckout}} that wraps the {{useCreateOneTimePurchaseCart}} data-access [hook|https://github.com/hellofresh/web/blob/master/app/data-access/one-time-purchase/create-one-time-purchase-cart.tsx]. 
This hook will gather all required parameters from Redux state and localStorage, transform them into the correct format, and provide a simple interface for the Payment page to create OTP carts during checkout.

*Background:*

* OTP (One-Time Purchase) products require cart creation via a different endpoint than subscription products
* The OTP cart creation requires specific parameters: product handle, delivery date/option, and product selections
* These parameters are scattered across Redux state, localStorage, and custom hooks
* This hook centralizes the logic to make Payment.js integration clean and simple
{panel}

